---
slug: "pricing"
permalink: "/en/pricing/index.html"
title: "Pricing reference | Morrison Premium Transfer"
description: "Reference prices by vehicle class and route type. Final price is locked in writing before departure."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Home", path: "/en/" }
  - { name: "Pricing", path: "/en/pricing/" }
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="kicker reveal-up">Pricing</p>
    <h1 class="reveal-up">Reference prices —<br>no surprises mid-route.</h1>
    <p class="lead reveal-up">The exact price is locked in writing before departure. Below — what to budget from.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="compare-wrap">
      <table class="compare-table pricing-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th></th>
            {%- for tier in pricing.tiers -%}
            <th>
              <span class="pricing-th-brand">{{ fleet.classes[loop.index0].tier }}</span>
              <span class="pricing-th-name">{{ tier.nameEn }}</span>
            </th>
            {%- endfor %}
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><th scope="row">Passengers</th>{%- for tier in pricing.tiers %}<td class="num">{{ tier.pax }}</td>{%- endfor %}</tr>
          <tr><th scope="row">Luggage</th>{%- for tier in pricing.tiers %}<td class="num">{{ tier.bags }}</td>{%- endfor %}</tr>
          <tr><th scope="row">City / airport from</th>{%- for tier in pricing.tiers %}<td class="num">R$ {{ tier.cityFromBrl }}</td>{%- endfor %}</tr>
          <tr><th scope="row">Intercity per km from</th>{%- for tier in pricing.tiers %}<td class="num">R$ {{ tier.intercityPerKmBrl }}</td>{%- endfor %}</tr>
          <tr><th scope="row">International per km from</th>{%- for tier in pricing.tiers %}<td class="num">R$ {{ tier.internationalPerKmBrl }}</td>{%- endfor %}</tr>
          <tr><th scope="row">Hourly from</th>{%- for tier in pricing.tiers %}<td class="num">R$ {{ tier.hourlyBrl }} / h</td>{%- endfor %}</tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--bg-soft">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2 style="text-align: center;">Included in every tariff</h2>
    <ul class="checklist" style="max-width: 640px; margin: 1.6rem auto 0;">
      <li>Driver, fuel, tolls and parking on the route</li>
      <li>Bottled water, USB charger, air-con</li>
      <li>Flight tracking by number (60 min free wait)</li>
      <li>NF-e for companies within 5 business days</li>
      <li>WhatsApp / Telegram with the driver before departure</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem;">Billed separately</h2>
    <ul class="checklist" style="max-width: 640px; margin: 1.6rem auto 0;">
      <li>Child seat (on request)</li>
      <li>Wi-Fi on long routes</li>
      <li>Extra stops beyond plan</li>
      <li>Night pickups (9 PM–6 AM) — +15%</li>
      <li>Holiday peak dates — discussed separately</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2>Quote a specific route?</h2>
    <div class="cta-strip-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="/en/#calculator">Open the calculator</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/en/contact/">Send a request</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
